# API Patterns Overview

## Architecture

Our API architecture follows a server function approach with TanStack Start:

- Type-safe server functions
- Request validation
- Error handling
- Security middleware
- Performance optimization

## Core Technologies

- TanStack Start for server functions
- Zod for validation
- TypeScript for type safety
- HTTP headers for security
- Rate limiting for protection

